Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:17.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}這樣的話將永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年無憂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:29.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論如何都想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:35.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夥伴們曾牽在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:42.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已變得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:46.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一個個漸漸離去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:53.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向著那甦醒之日
